{"tid":1432129,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"示威學生家人涉遭中共官員上門威嚇","createTime":"2019-08-08T07:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T07:46:56.000Z","uid":253003,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"facc56518d63e81c9d805f8cbc1c201ece11aec7","tid":1432129,"uid":253003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"一名不願透露姓名的昆士蘭大學生，曾在澳洲參與反逃犯條例示威活動，但不久後其中國家人被當地官員「登門拜訪」。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府涉嫌利用恐嚇手段，嚴密監控任何昆士蘭大學(University of Queensland)示威活動的參加者及記名，有自由黨議員指令人感到震驚。<br />\n<br />\n昆士蘭大學早前發起示威活動，聲援香港人反逃犯修訂條例及支持民主，並譴責北京鎮壓維吾爾少數民族。示威者一度佔領孔子學院，與支持共產黨的中國學生發生暴力衝突，影片被分享到社交媒體上。<br />\n<br />\n該名害怕被辨別的學生不願意透露姓名，他向《雪梨晨鋒報》及《時代報》表示，「我當時在示威中，但當他們拍片時我儘量隱藏臉部，或立即遠離人群」。但幾天內便接到母親從中國來電，指家中「有客到訪」，並遭警告持政治異見的潛在後果。<br />\n<br />\n他的母親遭當局警告兒子在布里斯本參與「違反中央」的活動，又警告他「不可再出席集會」。她向兒子說：「只要停止集會，才可確保自己和家人的安全」。她指家人向官員保證，兒子會永遠效忠共產黨。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲聯邦情報及安全委員會主席、兼自由黨議員希斯迪(Andrew Hastie)稱，他對此感到震驚。他說：「這正是聯盟黨政府2018年通過外國干涉法的原因，要保障離鄉別井的人免受外國勢力脅逼」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/student-attended-a-protest-at-an-australian-uni-chinese-officials-visited-his-family?fbclid=IwAR1Szd6CkfhaoQgflY14WDM98eMxrQci8p-gyFb_qS98OQhYGckKc9aSkJU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fstudent-attended-a-protest-at-an-australian-uni-chinese-officials-visited-his-family%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Szd6CkfhaoQgflY14WDM98eMxrQci8p-gyFb_qS98OQhYGckKc9aSkJU&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=92862ff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/student-attended-a-protest-at-an-australian-uni-chinese-officials-visited-his-family?fbclid=IwAR1Szd6CkfhaoQgflY14WDM98eMxrQci8p-gyFb_qS98OQhYGckKc9aSkJU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12ed3be1807d8f51ce950b01602d31434f98dcb","tid":1432129,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:18:33.000Z","msg":"CLS<br />\n<br />\n中國同胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43f214a17f27084e25e6942e1682a702cf0a1a6","tid":1432129,"uid":186668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:31:59.000Z","msg":"毛主席is watching you."},{"pid":"da3a81e9bc7dfe330a338242a733f62005f20bcd","tid":1432129,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258d0af56aa03cffac0396648472005b6a06e65b","tid":1432129,"uid":223295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa2781959c01d66ecede318d5ac7ba00a52c455","tid":1432129,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:42:13.000Z","msg":"與支持共產黨的中國學生發生暴力衝突<br />\nip都唔洗check<br />\n全部掟哂返支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065c400d286b3731ca60e166863d4b271a185ce2","tid":1432129,"uid":60484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:46:56.000Z","msg":"cls"}]}